<plot>On an ordinary day, a musician sends his son to daycare while he goes to compose on his instrument. However, his son keeps calling asking for various things, but his father ignores him. As the pleas keep coming and become more heartfelt, the musician's guilt and frustration inadvertently lead him to a flight of fancy that leads to a flight of musical inspiration for his son.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?142357</url></doc>
